folder: Stuyvesant Avenue & Chauncey Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Stuyvesant Avenue, east side, at Decatur and Bainbridge Streets. View 1 shows limestone houses at the southeast corner of Chauncey Street; view 2, a brownstone at the northeast corner of Bainbridge Street.
P. L. merr  August 27, 1941
Vuin ', V
